Package org.efaps.ci Description

The CI Classes (Configuration Items) are used for accessing types and their attributes from eFaps. The base class for all types is CIType. This classes are created automatically for the modules by an maven target using the eFaps maven plugin. Due to the hen - egg problem the classes in the kernel are created manually and not by the plugin. The class do not contain any comments and checkstyle is deactivated for them.
